{"word":"τότε","slug":"τότε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>τότε</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a> pronominal stem *to + <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ suff.\">suff.</a> -<el>τε</el>] demonstrative temporal <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> specifically of a time that is later or past <b>then <a href='B:530 13:12'>1 Cor 13:12</a>; <a href='B:650 12:26'>Hb 12:26</a>; <a href='B:680 3:6'>2 Pt 3:6</a>.</b> Most <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ reff.\">reff.</a> fit well under<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on a time or circumstance that is closely associated with what precedes in the narrative<b><p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp> at that time <a href='B:470 27:16'>Mt 27:16</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπὸ\">ἀπὸ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τότε\">τότε</a></el> from that time/since then <b><a href='B:470 26:16'>26:16</a>; <a href='B:490 16:16'>Lk 16:16</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp> then, thereupon <a href='B:470 2:17'>Mt 2:17</a>; <a href='B:470 4:1'>4:1</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Mt; <b><a href='B:480 2:20'>Mk 2:20</a>; <a href='B:480 13:14'>13:14</a>, <a href='B:480 13:21'>21</a>; <a href='B:490 5:35'>Lk 5:35</a>; <a href='B:490 11:26'>11:26</a>; <a href='B:490 21:27'>21:27</a>; <a href='B:490 24:45'>24:45</a>; <a href='B:500 11:6'>J 11:6</a>, <a href='B:500 11:14'>14</a>; <a href='B:500 12:16'>12:16</a>; <a href='B:500 19:1'>19:1</a>, <a href='B:500 19:16'>16</a>; <a href='B:500 20:8'>20:8</a>; <a href='B:510 1:12'>Ac 1:12</a>; <a href='B:510 17:14'>17:14</a>; <a href='B:530 4:5'>1 Cor 4:5</a>; <a href='B:540 12:10'>2 Cor 12:10</a>; <a href='B:550 4:8'>Gal 4:8</a></b> (enslavement linked with ignorance); <b><a href='B:590 5:3'>1 Th 5:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:τοσοῦτος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:τοὐναντίον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}